msgctxt "0001"
msgid "Hey Makoto, could you come with me for a second?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0002"
msgid "Huh? Where are we going?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0003"
msgid "My room. I wanna talk to you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0004"
msgid "In your room...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0005"
msgid "Just come with me..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0006"
msgid "O-Okay..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0007"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Mondo dragged me to his room.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0008"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgctxt "0009"
msgid "Listen, can I talk to you about something important?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0010"
msgid "Important...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0011"
msgid "It's kind of cheesy, but..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0012"
msgid ""
"...there isn't really anyone else here I can talk to\n"
"about this kinda stuff."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0013"
msgid ""
"I can't show weakness in front of my classmates, and\n"
"I've never had a friend on the same level as me..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0014"
msgid "So...do you mind?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0015"
msgid "Yeah, I mean if you're okay talking to me..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0016"
msgid "Listen, do you like being a high schooler?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0017"
msgid ""
"Huh? Sure, it's fun. But why are you asking that out\n"
"of the blue like this?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0018"
msgid ""
"I like it too, ya know. I like screwin' around with my\n"
"friends and stuff."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0019"
msgid ""
"Whenever I get to go out and run wild with my Crazy\n"
"Diamond crew, it's such a goddamn rush..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0020"
msgid ""
"I mean sure, there was a shit-ton of pressure to build\n"
"up the gang and everything, but still..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0021"
msgid "Gettin' to hang with them was the fuckin' best, man."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0022"
msgid "But I've been thinking a lot lately..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0023"
msgid "What's gonna happen when I'm done with high school?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0024"
msgid ""
"Everyone in the Crazy Diamonds is gonna graduate. I\n"
"gave everything to them. What do I do then?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0025"
msgid "And I'm not smart like the rest of you..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0026"
msgid "College? Not a chance. So I gotta get a job, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0027"
msgid ""
"I feel like...maybe I've already done whatever I'm\n"
"gonna do in life. Maybe I've maxed out..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0028"
msgid ""
"It's like I'm...empty now. I dunno, I can't figure out\n"
"how to say it..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0029"
msgid ""
"The point is, that's how big a part of my life\n"
"the Crazy Diamonds have been."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0030"
msgid ""
"So when I think about not having that around\n"
"anymore..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0031"
msgid "...I get <CLT 3>scared<CLT>."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0032"
msgid ""
"Maybe that's why I came here in the first place,\n"
"to run away."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0033"
msgid "To run away from the fear..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0034"
msgid "Mondo..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0035"
msgid ""
"And maybe this is my punishment for everything up till\n"
"now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0036"
msgid ""
"Maybe I'm being punished for just doing whatever I\n"
"felt like all my life."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0037"
msgid "I don't think that's what this is..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0038"
msgid ""
"I think you're lucky to have something you're so\n"
"passionate about."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0039"
msgid ""
"Being able to get into something that much... I'm sure\n"
"that'll be useful later on in life."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0040"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgctxt "0041"
msgid ""
"Shit, Makoto. You want me to put on a suit or some\n"
"shit?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0042"
msgid "But...maybe you're right..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0043"
msgid ""
"Maybe having as much fun as I did, means I'll be able\n"
"to dedicate myself to working hard from now on."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0044"
msgid ""
"You know, when I think about it...maybe it won't be\n"
"all that bad!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0045"
msgid ""
"Maybe I'm even starting to look forward to the idea of\n"
"working. Just a little..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0046"
msgid "So, what kind of job would you want to get?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0047"
msgid "Oh, I wanna be a <CLT 3>carpenter<CLT> for sure!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0048"
msgid ""
"I figure, I've done such a good job of busting shit\n"
"apart, I'd prolly be good at building it, too!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0049"
msgid ""
"Just watch! I'm gonna become the best carpenter you've\n"
"ever seen!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0050"
msgid "Well, it's you, so I'm sure you can do it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0051"
msgid "Course, that means we gotta get outta here first..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0052"
msgid "Well, as long as we work hard and don't give up..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0053"
msgid "Yeah, you're right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0054"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I'm glad I got to talk to Mondo like this.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0055"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I feel like I've come to understand Mondo a lot\n"
"better...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0056"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I think we've finally become <CLT><CLT 3>friends<CLT><CLT 4> in the truest\n"
"sense of the word.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0057"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>Mondo's <CLT><CLT 3>Report Card<CLT><CLT 23> has been updated based on your\n"
"experience with him.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0058"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>Your maximum number of <CLT><CLT 3>Skill Points<CLT><CLT 23> has increased!\n"
"Hey, look at you go!\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0059"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I talked with Mondo a little bit longer, then went\n"
"back to my room.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""
